title: Black Flag T2 T3 (2012) (Sosich)cbr
description:
Captain Dark Dan and his companions are in bad situation.Pirate ship'Black Joke'has thrown anchor off the coast of an unknown island,revealed by a map that Dark Dan acquired from a mysterious aristocrat for few drops of his blood.
As the leader of his crew,Dan sinks into the heart of the island,looking for a treasure he knows nothing about,when an unlikely phenomenon hapens.A gigahtic building with inconcevable architecture appears in front of them,like it sprung from nothingness!
Accompanied by Killing Howie,Dark Dan enters the strange building that immediatly disappears like it was absorbed by a mist...

enjoy
